sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Administrator
    participant CLI as kubectl-odh<br/>(odh-cli binary)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DSC as DataScienceCluster<br/>(singleton CR)
    participant DSCI as DSCInitialization<br/>(singleton CR)
    participant OLM as OLM Resources<br/>(Subscriptions/CSVs)
    participant Workloads as Workload CRs<br/>(Notebooks, ISVCs, etc.)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Admin,GitHub: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment

    Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh lint [--checks=...]
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC spec + status
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSCInitialization<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSCI spec + status
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Subscriptions, CSVs<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: OLM operator states
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks, InferenceServices,<br/>ServingRuntimes, DSPAs, RayClusters,<br/>PyTorchJobs, ClusterQueues, etc.<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Workload resources
    Note over CLI: Execute 37 checks<br/>5 groups (dependency, service,<br/>platform, component, workload)<br/>Version-aware gating
    CLI-->>Admin: DiagnosticResults<br/>(table/JSON/YAML)<br/>Impact: Prohibited > Blocking > Advisory

    Note over Admin,GitHub: Flow 2: Backup Workloads

    Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh backup [--namespace=...]
    CLI->>K8sAPI: Discovery: LIST workloads<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Discovered resources
    Note over CLI: Concurrent pipeline<br/>(Discovery → Resolver → Writer)
    CLI->>K8sAPI: Resolve dependencies<br/>(ConfigMaps, Secrets, PVCs)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Dependency resources
    CLI->>FS: Write YAML files<br/>(organized by namespace/type)
    CLI-->>Admin: Backup summary

    Note over Admin,GitHub: Flow 3: Migration (Kueue → RHBOK)

    Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate prepare kueue-to-rhbok
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterQueues, LocalQueues,<br/>ConfigMaps<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Current resources
    CLI->>FS: Write backup YAML files
    CLI-->>Admin: Prepare complete

    Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate run kueue-to-rhbok
    CLI->>K8sAPI: CREATE OLM Subscription (RHBOK)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Subscription created
    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH ConfigMaps<br/>(reconciliation annotation)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: ConfigMaps annotated
    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH DataScienceCluster<br/>(managementState)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC patched
    CLI->>K8sAPI: Verify resources preserved<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Verification results
    CLI-->>Admin: Migration result<br/>(step-by-step progress)

    Note over Admin,GitHub: Flow 4: Dependency Manifest Refresh (optional)

    Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh deps --refresh
    CLI->>GitHub: GET odh-gitops/values.yaml<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>No auth (public)
    GitHub-->>CLI: Dependency manifest YAML
    CLI-->>Admin: Dependency status table
